cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper is about deep learning with Hebbian updates, which is a topic related to neural networks and their training. Therefore, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also focuses on image datasets, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper proposes a new cost function, which is related to machine learning and optimization, and could place it in cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses the biologically plausible aspects of the proposed method, which could make it relevant to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
